==English==

===Noun===
'''[[independent]] [[variable]]''' (''plural'' '''[[independent variables]]''')

# {{algebra}} In an [[equation]], any variable whose value is not dependent on any other in the equation.
#:''In the equation z = x<sup>2</sup> + y, x and y are the independent variables.''
# {{science}} The variable that is changed in an experment.

